primary_efficacy_outcome: Incidence of objectively confirmed recurrent Venous Thromboembolism (VTE), a composite endpoint comprising proximal Deep Vein Thrombosis (DVT) of the lower limbs (symptomatic or unsuspected), symptomatic DVT of the upper limb, and Pulmonary Embolism (PE) (symptomatic or unsuspected).
secondary_efficacy_outcomes: Individual components of the primary efficacy outcome
